        <item>
            <title>DJI 取消美国地理围栏功能，将控制权交还用家</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 15:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dji]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无人机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287309</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>DJI 无人机一向有地理围栏功能，阻止用家将无人机飞进禁飞区域，不过他们最近公布在美国取消相关功能，只会显示可以关闭的警告来代替。<br /><span id="more-1287309"></span></p><p>DJI 全球政策主管 Adam Welsh 表示，由于美国已实施遥距识别（Remote ID）等监管措施，让执法部门拥有执行现有规则的工具，因此公司决定「将控制权还给无人机操作者」，不再强行阻碍用家飞行。</p><p>不过近来美国对无人机安全忧虑增加，之前加州大火更出现无人机干扰救援的事件，加上即将举办总统就职典礼，有意见认为 DJI 新政策的推出时机值得商榷。DJI 方面在官方网志中就强调，此决定与政治无关，称原计划数月前就要推出此更新。而 FAA 发言人 Ian Gregor 则表示，联邦航空管理局确实不要求无人机制造商实施地理围栏功能，但此项自愿性的安全措施移除是否会影响航空安全，仍有待观察。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://viewpoints.dji.com/blog/djis-geo-system-is-an-education-not-enforcement-tool">DJI</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>任天堂 Switch 2 正式亮相，官方影片揭露新机设计与功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nitendo-switch-2-news</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 14:04:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nitendo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287427</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>众所期待的任天堂 Switch 2 终于揭开神秘面纱。任天堂官方于今晚无预警释出相关影片，新机外观及多项新功能正式公开。</p><p>自 2017 年推出 Nintendo Switch 以来，这款游戏机已进入第 8 年，不少玩家早已期待其后继机型的到来。任天堂曾表示，会在本财年内公开 Switch 2 消息，而在多次传闻与爆料后，1 月 16 日晚间 9 点，官方终于于 YouTube 平台公开长达 2 分钟的影片，让全球粉丝抢先目睹 Switch 2 的外貌与设计。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Switch 2 的外观延续一代设计风格，但加入了多项改进细节。机身四周的接口重新调整，并新增更方便的 Type-C 插孔于主机上方，背面采用全新直立架设计，提供多角度摆放功能。控制器部分，摇杆与按钮均增大以提升操作舒适度，背部更增设按钮，可作为滑鼠功能使用。此外，Switch 2 预计于 2025 年内正式推出，并将于 4 月 2 日举办 Nintendo Direct 发表会进一步揭露更多细节。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233-694x330.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="330" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233-694x330.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>任天堂同时强调，Switch 2 将支援向下相容，玩家可继续游玩目前的 Nintendo Switch 游戏软体，并选择体验现有游戏中的下一款作品。Nintendo Switch Online 服务亦会延续支援至新机型上，为玩家提供更完善的游戏体验。</p><p><iframe title="YouTube video player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S1CbhpKC6SE?si=egpMrJM8JU4lnyCr" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>来源: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1CbhpKC6SE">nintendo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Blue Origin 新型火箭首飞成功，将成 SpaceX Falcon Heavy 竞争对手</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[BLUE ORIGIN]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287296</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Jeff Bezos 旗下的 Blue Origin 全新研发的 New Glenn 火箭最近终于成功首飞，这款高达 320 呎的运载火箭预计将会与 SpaceX 的 Falcon Heavy 直接竞争，也为客户带来更多选择。<br /><span id="more-1287296"></span></p><p>New Glenn 火箭搭载了 7 具可重复使用 BE-4 引擎的 NG-1 火箭点火升空，二级火箭与载荷，在美国东部时间凌晨 2 点 03 分成功进入轨道，达成首飞主要任务目标。不过今次首飞也并非完美，火箭一级助推器在执行回收任务时，突然失去通讯并停止传送数据，最终 Blue Origin 证实助推器在降落过程中遗失。不过总裁 Dave Limp 在发射前已经表示，本次无人飞行任务的首要目标是进入轨道，其他目标皆为「额外收获」。</p><p>New Glenn 火箭历经近十年的研发，运载能力与 SpaceX 的 Falcon Heavy 相当，未来将主要用于货运任务。其中最受瞩目的是为 Blue Origin 的 Project Kuiper 衞星网路计划服务，预计发射 3,236 颗衞星，与 SpaceX 的 Starlink 竞争。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.space.com/space-exploration/launches-spacecraft/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket-into-orbit-on-1st-flight-video">Space.com</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/">Blue Origin 新型火箭首飞成功，将成 SpaceX Falcon Heavy 竞争对手</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教学】iPhone 动态岛显示农历 + 天气，一个 app 令动态岛显示不同实用资讯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/iphone-dynamic-island-weather/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-dynamic-island-weather</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/iphone-dynamic-island-weather/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[动态岛]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287164</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>最近小编身边的朋友都纷纷升级至 iPhone 16，小编自己也从 iPhone 13 mini 升级至 iPhone 16，尚未太习惯动态岛存在。今日小编想和大家分享一下如何活用动态岛，让你可以随时检视天气、农历日期等资讯。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0116" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1047394327?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>Step 1 安装「锁屏启动」应用程式</h2><p>要改变动态岛显示资讯，无须 Jailbreak，你只需要安装「锁屏启动」应用程式（<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E9%8E%96%E5%B1%8F%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95-%E8%90%AC%E8%83%BD%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E4%BB%B6-%E9%9D%88%E5%8B%95%E5%B3%B6%E4%B8%80%E9%8D%B5%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91%E4%BD%88%E5%B1%80/id1636719674">下载连结</a>）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安装「锁屏启动」程式</p><p>启用应用程式后，会显示下面画面。记得要点击右上角的「x」，<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>不要选择免费试用</strong></span>，否则 3 天后将会开始收费。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不要点击「免费试用」</p><h2>Step 2 设定动态岛</h2><p>之完成上述设定后会跳页至下图画面，点击右上角的星星图案，然后选择「开／关动态岛」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先点击右上角「✨」（绿框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「开／关动态岛」</p><p>接下来你需要开启「灵活岛＆即时活动」，预设为关闭。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲启用「灵活岛＆即时活动」</p><p>接下来向下滑动至「资料设定动态岛」（红框示），分别设定「左侧显示」与「右侧显示」选项，将选项改为「农历（万年历）」以及「当前天气」资讯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲分别设定左右则显示</p><p>先点击「左侧显示」，进入设定页面后向下滑动至看见「农历（万年历）」并点击之。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「左侧显示」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「农历（万年历）」</p><p>之后点击「右侧显示」，向下滑动至看见「当前天气」再点击该选项，最后按「完成」储存设定。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「右侧显示」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「当前天气」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击完成方会储存选项</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
